author: Stephanie Anderson
title: Live: Are hackers targeting our politicians?
text:
By political reporter Stephanie Anderson Updated February 15, 2017 09:11:07 Map: Australia 
Australia's political parties have been formally briefed by intelligence agencies on the threat posed by foreign cyber attacks. 
The confidential and unprecedented briefings took place at Parliament House yesterday following revelations Russia ordered a hidden campaign to influence last year's US presidential election. 
Follow live.
